      <title>欧盟缓解气体存储要求以避免价格峰值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/eu-to-seek-two-year-extension-to-controversial-gas-storage-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲联盟今年正在放松填充天然气储存的要求，使各国在达到该地区11月1日的目标时有一些摆动的空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/eu-to-seek-two-year-extension-to-controversial-gas-storage-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 09:21:19 GMT</pubDate>
